{"id": "ChIJ-903TwCBhYARPutXiPynjkI", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 19, "displayName": {"text": "Bape Store San Francisco", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ-903TwCBhYARPutXiPynjkI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tneGQyMWFaRmQ1ZWxkelJHOUVVbmxGYUVVMFNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "OG streetwear brand BAPEs long awaited store in San Francisco is finally open! With local handpicked boutique curator employees, it makes your visit feel personal. As soon as you walk in you are greeted with lines of their signature camos stacked throughout their two story complex. Now those fast, online, sold out drops can be obtained with more ease! Can't wait for future line ups with the homies!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "OG streetwear brand BAPEs long awaited store in San Francisco is finally open! With local handpicked boutique curator employees, it makes your visit feel personal. As soon as you walk in you are greeted with lines of their signature camos stacked throughout their two story complex. Now those fast, online, sold out drops can be obtained with more ease! Can't wait for future line ups with the homies!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ethan Palma", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107774325734301486936/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8Y22eW7KjYtLSgLg1PaNuwf9xTT4skHW5iVB3RTxtaDfCA-E8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T15:13:19.411685357Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tneGQyMWFaRmQ1ZWxkelJHOUVVbmxGYUVVMFNFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tneGQyMWFaRmQ1ZWxkelJHOUVVbmxGYUVVMFNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x808581004f37ddfb:0x428ea7fc8857eb3e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-903TwCBhYARPutXiPynjkI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tNek9ISlNWVjgzWjNOcWFFTndaRzlMZWxscVRuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My boyfriend and I came from the East Coast to visit some friends and we stopped by the new BAPE location and absolutely loved the staff! Everyone was super friendly and welcoming, and they helped us with everything we needed without hesitation. Special thanks to Basil for being extra attentive and friendly!! He went above and beyond to make our visit memorable and made us feel genuinely welcomed as customers. His customer service, positive attitude, and knowledge of the brand really stood out to us. I hope this feedback can be shared with him and that he receives the recognition he deserves because employees like Basil are what make the shopping experience special.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My boyfriend and I came from the East Coast to visit some friends and we stopped by the new BAPE location and absolutely loved the staff! Everyone was super friendly and welcoming, and they helped us with everything we needed without hesitation. Special thanks to Basil for being extra attentive and friendly!! He went above and beyond to make our visit memorable and made us feel genuinely welcomed as customers. His customer service, positive attitude, and knowledge of the brand really stood out to us. I hope this feedback can be shared with him and that he receives the recognition he deserves because employees like Basil are what make the shopping experience special.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "heather kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100822006507714721052/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzGgjjPCf14Vs6kqsr4lQEQoiy5WJKwGVURznnoN0VOY9nsj02Mw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-17T00:43:58.551051845Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tNek9ISlNWVjgzWjNOcWFFTndaRzlMZWxs